### DormBedInvoice/Create
POST {{host}}/api/Hotel/DormBedInvoice/Create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "apiKey": "{{apiKey}}",
  "token": "{{token}}",
  "debtAmount": 1500000,
  "creditorAmount": 0,
  "paidAmount": 0,
  "penaltyAmount": 0,
  "penaltyPrecentEveryDate": 2,
  "contractId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "dueDate": "2026-08-01T00:00:00Z",
  "tags": [102, 204]
}

